channel.title: Question for Joel Nielsen
channel.description: A few years ago, there used to be a track on youtube (if I remember correctly) titled Demo 3. It sounded quite Half-Livesy/Black Mesaie (at least in my head), but the video got made private or even possibly deleted and I couldn't find it anywhere else since. It's not on you official website among the other 'demos' Rings any bells? If so, why isn't it uploaded anywhere anymore?
